contents:
[package]
name = "roon-api"
version = "0.3.1"
authors = [ "The Appgineer",]
license-file = "LICENSE"
readme = "README.md"
repository = "https://github.com/theappgineer/rust-roon-api"
edition = "2021"
publish = false

[dependencies]
futures-util = "0.3"
tokio-tungstenite = "0.21.0"
if-addrs = "0.13.1"
url = "2.2.2"
serde_json = "1.0"
typetag = "0.2"
regex = "1.5.5"
log = "0.4"

[dev-dependencies]
simple-logging = "2.0"

[features]
pairing = []
status = []
settings = []
image = []
transport = [ "pairing",]
browse = [ "pairing",]
default = []

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.24.1"
features = [ "io-std", "macros", "rt", "sync", "time",]

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "1.2.2"
features = [ "v4",]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "derive",]
